---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="Brainspotting Therapy in Walnut Creek, CA | Oakland Brainspotting Therapy"
	description="Certified Brainspotting therapist serving Walnut Creek, CA. Trauma, anxiety, and grief treatment. In-person Oakland office and telehealth sessions available."
>
	<main class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-50 to-white">
		<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-primary-900 text-white">
			<div class="container-custom">
				<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
					<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
						Brainspotting Therapy in Walnut Creek, CA
					</h1>
					<p class="text-xl text-primary-100 leading-relaxed mb-8">
						Certified Brainspotting therapist serving Walnut Creek and Contra Costa County. Brain-based trauma therapy with telehealth and in-person options.
					</p>
					<a href="https://megan-gredesky.clientsecure.me" target="_blank" class="btn btn-accent text-xl px-12 py-5 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
						Schedule Consultation →
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="py-16">
			<div class="container-custom">
				<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-6">Brainspotting Therapy for Walnut Creek Residents</h2>
					
					<p class="text-lg text-warm-800 leading-relaxed mb-6">
						Oakland Brainspotting Therapy provides specialized trauma treatment for Walnut Creek residents. While our office is in Oakland, we offer convenient telehealth sessions for Walnut Creek clients throughout California.
					</p>

					<p class="text-lg text-warm-800 leading-relaxed mb-8">
						Whether you're dealing with trauma, anxiety, grief, or performance issues, Brainspotting offers a powerful alternative to traditional talk therapy for Walnut Creek residents.
					</p>

					<div class="bg-primary-50 p-8 rounded-lg mb-8">
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-4">Why Walnut Creek Residents Choose Brainspotting</h3>
						<ul class="space-y-3">
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
									<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
								</svg>
								<span class="text-warm-800"><strong>Telehealth convenience:</strong> No commute - meet from your Walnut Creek home</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
									<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
								</svg>
								<span class="text-warm-800"><strong>In-person option:</strong> Oakland office accessible via BART + short bus ride</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
									<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
								</svg>
								<span class="text-warm-800"><strong>Evidence-based:</strong> Certified Brainspotting practitioner with 9+ years experience</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex gap-3">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
									<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
								</svg>
								<span class="text-warm-800"><strong>Flexible scheduling:</strong> Evening and weekend appointments available</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="py-16 bg-white">
			<div class="container-custom">
				<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-12 text-center">Common Issues We Treat in Walnut Creek</h2>
					
					<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
						<div class="bg-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-4">Work-Related Stress</h3>
							<p class="text-warm-700 mb-4">
								Walnut Creek professionals dealing with burnout, work stress, and career transitions find Brainspotting helps restore balance.
							</p>
							<a href="/anxiety" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium">
								Learn about anxiety treatment →
							</a>
						</div>

						<div class="bg-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-4">Trauma & PTSD</h3>
							<p class="text-warm-700 mb-4">
								Effective trauma processing for Walnut Creek residents seeking healing without having to relive traumatic experiences.
							</p>
							<a href="/trauma" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium">
								Learn about trauma treatment →
							</a>
						</div>

						<div class="bg-primary-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
							<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-4">Performance Enhancement</h3>
							<p class="text-warm-700 mb-4">
								Athletes, performers, and professionals use Brainspotting to overcome blocks and enhance performance.
							</p>
							<a href="/performers" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium">
								Learn about performance enhancement →
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="py-16 bg-primary-50">
			<div class="container-custom">
				<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-6">Telehealth & In-Person Options</h2>
					
					<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-soft mb-8">
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-4">Telehealth (Recommended for Walnut Creek)</h3>
						<p class="text-warm-800 leading-relaxed mb-4">
							Most Walnut Creek clients prefer our secure telehealth sessions. Meet from the comfort of your home with the same effective Brainspotting therapy.
						</p>
						<ul class="space-y-2 text-warm-700">
							<li>• No commute time</li>
							<li>• Flexible scheduling</li>
							<li>• Same effectiveness as in-person</li>
							<li>• HIPAA-compliant video platform</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-soft">
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-900 mb-4">In-Person Option (Oakland Office)</h3>
						<p class="text-lg mb-4">
							<strong>3637 Grand Ave</strong><br>
							Oakland, CA 94609
						</p>
						
						<h4 class="font-bold text-primary-900 mb-2 mt-6">From Walnut Creek:</h4>
						<ul class="space-y-2 text-warm-700">
							<li>• <strong>By BART:</strong> Walnut Creek → 19th St Oakland, then AC Transit Line 12 to Grand Ave</li>
							<li>• <strong>By car:</strong> 30-40 minutes via I-580 or CA-24</li>
							<li>• <strong>Parking:</strong> Street parking available</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="py-16 bg-primary-900 text-white">
			<div class="container-custom text-center">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Start Healing?</h2>
				<p class="text-xl text-primary-100 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
					Schedule a free 15-minute consultation to learn how Brainspotting can help you.
				</p>
				<div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
					<a href="https://megan-gredesky.clientsecure.me" target="_blank" class="btn btn-accent text-xl px-12 py-5 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
						Schedule Consultation
					</a>
					<a href="tel:5105563699" class="btn bg-white text-primary-900 hover:bg-primary-50 text-xl px-12 py-5 shadow-lg">
						Call (510) 556-3699
					</a>
				</div>
				<p class="text-primary-200 mt-6">
					Serving Walnut Creek, Concord, Pleasant Hill, and Contra Costa County
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
